Product Information


Product Ordering
Order by Phone
ReliantHeart processes all orders. Orders may be directed to ReliantHeart at:
ReliantHeart Inc.
8965 Interchange
Houston, TX  77054
United States
Phone: (713) 592-0913
Fax: (713) 665-0963
The lines are available weekdays (excluding national holidays) between 8:00 a.m. and 6:00 p.m. CST.
Online Ordering
To enter orders in a more efficient and cost effective manner, ReliantHeart provides secure online order entry. Orders are processed automatically and immediately.
To register for online ordering, please contact us.

Product Support
All ReliantHeart products are fully supported by our clinical support staff.
Design Changes
ReliantHeart reserves the right to change or discontinue any product without notice. Additionally, if the product has been discontinued, we most likely will have produced a more desirable alternative.
Product Code or Description
If you Login to order online, the product reference code will be automatically entered during the ordering process. Ordering online will simplify the ordering process and improve order accuracy.
For assistance in obtaining product information or product catalogs please call ReliantHeart at (713) 592-0913.
Damaged HeartAssist5® VAD
In the rare event that the HeartAssist5® is dropped or damaged in the sterile field please consult your clinical representative for alternatives available to you.
Please use the following address for all returns:
ReliantHeart Inc.
Attn: Returned Goods Department
8965 Interchange
Houston, TX  77054
United States
 


 

